{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a5c2f511af","title":"来取打圈子办法迷惑敌人","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a40afa257","index":0,"year":1946,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"a5c2f511af"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e84f82ab3e","name":"王震","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5ac33340ba","type":"paragraph","text":"来取打圈子办法迷惑敌人口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a5c2f511af"},{"id":"e07171a516","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月24日）王震：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a5c2f511af"},{"id":"2ee35cff3f","type":"paragraph","text":"你们如过分疲劳，似宜在陇海路、西兰路”之间采取打圈子办法，即向西又忽然向东，向北又忽然向南，如此可以迷惑敌人，取得短时休息，然后突过西兰路入边区。如何，望按情的定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a5c2f511af"},{"id":"8d4cc9b07d","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a5c2f511af"},{"id":"da305b67b0","type":"paragraph","text":"未敬口这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给中原军区副司令员兼参谋长王震的电报。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a5c2f511af"}],"page":{"id":"2073ab5966","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a5c2f511af","start":93,"end":93}}}},"__N_SSG":true}